### 3. Get all products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

### 4. Get product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1

### 5. Get products by team
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/team/Ferrari

### 6. Get products by driver
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/driver/Charles Leclerc

### 7. Update product
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productName": "Ferrari 2024 Team Shirt - Updated",
  "price": 95.99,
  "team": "Ferrari",
  "driver": "Charles Leclerc",
  "size": "L",
  "description": "Updated description for the Ferrari team shirt."
}

### 8. Delete product
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1

### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
